      <p begin="00:12:41.867" end="00:12:43.367">light lager, di cui</p>
      <p begin="00:12:43.433" end="00:12:45.200">la Budweiser e la Bud light sono</p>
      <p begin="00:12:45.267" end="00:12:45.967">gli esempi migliori.</p>
      <p begin="00:12:46.033" end="00:12:47.300">Quei marchi devono costantemente</p>
