      <p begin="00:12:53.367" end="00:12:56.467">[grugniti, ululati]</p>
      <p begin="00:12:56.533" end="00:12:57.433">[silenzio]</p>
      <p begin="00:12:57.500" end="00:12:58.833">[scoreggie di cavalli]</p>
      <p begin="00:12:58.900" end="00:12:59.533">Oh!</p>
      <p begin="00:12:59.600" end="00:13:01.533">Le altre birre si somigliano</p>
